[
    {
        "content": "<p>Is there a way to rewrite <em>specific</em> have in goal without manually writing meta code?</p>\n<p>Here is small example.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">):</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">10</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mul_comm</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">trace_state</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mul_assoc</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>This works well if I rewrite globally. But is there a way to rewrite specific <code>have</code> / <code>let</code> inside a goal?</p>",
        "id": 568672364,
        "sender_full_name": "Pavel Klimov",
        "timestamp": 1768750997
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>You can try selecting specific <code>let</code>/<code>have</code> with the <code>conv</code> mode.</p>",
        "id": 568675250,
        "sender_full_name": "Jakub Nowak",
        "timestamp": 1768752157
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Like this for example. Though, I didn't find a way to select <code>have</code> by its variable name</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">10</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">conv</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mul_comm</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mul_assoc</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">only</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">reduceMul</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 568675779,
        "sender_full_name": "Jakub Nowak",
        "timestamp": 1768752688
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Thanks for a reply. But in my case the have expression is way too long and I don't want to copy-paste it in the code.</p>",
        "id": 568676183,
        "sender_full_name": "Pavel Klimov",
        "timestamp": 1768753077
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Do you know about <code>conv?</code> in Mathlib? Then you can select terms by shift-click.</p>",
        "id": 568676590,
        "sender_full_name": "Kevin Buzzard",
        "timestamp": 1768753542
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>this is one of the fun ones because there's no way to fill in an <code>enter [...]</code> string that navigates into the value of a <code>let</code> or <code>have</code></p>",
        "id": 568676684,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1768753624
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"110038\">Kevin Buzzard</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/270676-lean4/topic/rewriting.20have.20in.20goal/near/568676590\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Do you know about <code>conv?</code> in Mathlib? Then you can select terms by shift-click.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I didn't. But it looks like it doesn't work \"Rpc error: InternalError: conv mode does not yet support entering let values\"</p>",
        "id": 568676715,
        "sender_full_name": "Jakub Nowak",
        "timestamp": 1768753653
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>and this is just a limitation of <code>enter [...]</code></p>",
        "id": 568676776,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1768753706
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"900336\">Pavel Klimov</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/270676-lean4/topic/rewriting.20have.20in.20goal/near/568676183\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Thanks for a reply. But in my case the have expression is way too long and I don't want to copy-paste it in the code.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>You don't have to copy-paste in entire expression. You can try to make an unambiguous pattern:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">10</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">conv</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mul_comm</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mul_assoc</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">only</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">reduceMul</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>or</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">10</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">conv</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mul_comm</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mul_assoc</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">only</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">reduceMul</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
